s `setInteractive({ useHandCursor: true })`. But the event listeners (`pointerov
er`, `pointerout`, `pointerdown`, `pointerup`, `pointerupoutside`) were already 
attached in `setupInteraction()`. In Phaser, `disableInteractive()` removes the 
input handler but doesn\'t remove the event listeners. When `setInteractive()` i
s called again, the old listeners are still there and will fire. So this is fine
.\n\n27. **Minor - `UIPanel` overlay click doesn\'t check which mouse button**:\
